{"tid":716222,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[贏国大把錢] 投資有出無入　一帶一路惹黨內質疑","createTime":"2018-06-25T05:39:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-26T11:28:33.000Z","uid":141151,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"fe6dffa4a1f8567fa43b7513e5e9b5dd429f93b1","tid":716222,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T05:39:04.000Z","msg":"投資有出無入　一帶一路惹黨內質疑<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/apple/a.php?i=20180625&amp;sec_id=15335&amp;s=0&amp;a=20430766\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Fapple%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180625%26sec_id%3D15335%26s%3D0%26a%3D20430766&d=KDvxH2Iy4rGunkJc4pLefIzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=081256d1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Fapple%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180625%26sec_id%3D15335%26s%3D0%26a%3D20430766&h=f4942912\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/apple/a.php?i=20180625&amp;sec_id=15335&amp;s=0&amp;a=20430766</a><br />\n<br />\n時事評論員劉銳紹對《蘋果》記者表示，中共事隔4年再開外事工作會議，在目前中美磨擦不斷升級、中國推行大國外交遇到不少問題背景下，的確值得外界關注；會議中共七常委出席，規模也超常，顯示會議的重要。<br />\n<br />\n劉銳紹︰或放慢執行<br />\n<br />\n劉銳紹指，中國發展到今時今日，不再走鄧小平韜光養晦之路，要搞大國外交，挑戰美國的世界霸主地位，尤其在東北亞、東南亞等地區，中美利益爭鬥激烈，所以要統一思想，統一行動；要令涉外高官們明瞭北京在想甚麼、要做甚麼；當然他們也要回國「照肺」。他續指，習在會上首次自己為自己總結出「10大外交思想」，今次會議獲確立其在中共外事工作的指導地位；「其實，習在外交工作並無獨創，習同江澤民一樣，不過是利用處理外交事件自我包裝。所謂10大外交思想，其實都係前朝遺物，習翻炒變成自己的。」<br />\n<br />\n他表示，過去5年中共急功近利，力推一帶一路，不但向西方，甚至向東伸到南美洲，引起美國和西方警惕中國有戰略野心；同時也因頻出現投資損失，引起中央黨內質疑聲四起，「我估計這次會議很可能要重新檢討有關做法，放慢或緩行」。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">習倡導的一帶一路戰略沿線涉及60多個國家。資料顯示，過去5年中共在一帶一路國家投入資金近萬億人民幣，其中至少五分之一受損失，不少項目爛尾，投資無法回籠。</span>"},{"pid":"7c590f8871ff0593ded49ba5e44f211f453c8efe","tid":716222,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T06:04:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/goal.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4935bbebd77de6d8d5804f1324ca86354829927d","tid":716222,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T12:39:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/42.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cac1691c016d181ec4b0d834318b281db433c413","tid":716222,"uid":108337,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T12:51:13.000Z","msg":"60多個窮撚國家可以點搾出錢?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15ec30b8ca7121f55b814649650bf5d53c88f346","tid":716222,"uid":58552,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T12:52:38.000Z","msg":"四個字<br />\n施惠遠鄰"},{"pid":"8032d4b119be6c26ab90ea56990e3ed15a11a04e","tid":716222,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cac1691c016d181ec4b0d834318b281db433c413","tid":716222,"uid":108337,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T12:51:13.000Z","msg":"60多個窮撚國家可以點搾出錢?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T12:54:02.000Z","msg":"當做下善事囉"},{"pid":"d366af519a709c76ab5a5ea03425a8b0dda8771d","tid":716222,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T12:54:21.000Z","msg":"送錢比人使<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5258a608d3124370019434267bbf5f642390a84f","tid":716222,"uid":44486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cac1691c016d181ec4b0d834318b281db433c413","tid":716222,"uid":108337,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T12:51:13.000Z","msg":"60多個窮撚國家可以點搾出錢?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T12:54:32.000Z","msg":"成個國家幫贏國打一世工<br />\n贏國又可以輸出過多既產能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97f02670ecc2c409c46b6dc332ce646be93e8af1","tid":716222,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5258a608d3124370019434267bbf5f642390a84f","tid":716222,"uid":44486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cac1691c016d181ec4b0d834318b281db433c413","tid":716222,"uid":